defaultAbout learning disabilitydefaultA learning disability is caused by the way t
defaulthe brain develops before, during or shortly after birth. It is always lifelong and affects someone's intellectual and social development. It used to be called mental handicap but this term is outdated and offensive. Learning disability is 
defaultnot
default a mental illn
defaultess. The term learning difficulty is often incorrectly used interchangeably with learning disability.
